@startuml
participant "IoT Device" as IoT
participant "RabbitMQ Broker" as RMQ
participant "Nuclio Function (Producer)" as Producer
participant "Nuclio Function (Consumer)" as Consumer
participant "Logger" as Logger

IoT -> RMQ: Send temperature data (MQTT/AMQP)
RMQ -> Producer: Trigger event
Producer -> Producer: Generate temperature event
Producer -> RMQ: Publish event to queue/topic
RMQ -> Consumer: Trigger event processing
Consumer -> Consumer: Process temperature data
Consumer -> RMQ: Publish processed data
RMQ -> Logger: Consume processed data
Logger -> Logger: Log data to console
@enduml